OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPowers for ministers       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funveiled in new strike laws
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Business Secretary Grant Shapps has set
OL,6, out plans to enforce minimum service   
OL,7, levels during strike action, including 
OL,8, for ambulance staff, firefighters and  
OL,9, railway workers.                       
OL,11,FUnder the bill, some employees would be
OL,12,Frequired to work during a strike and   
OL,13,Fcould be sacked if they refuse.        
OL,15,FMr Shapps said the aim was to protect  
OL,16,Flives and livelihoods.                 
OL,18,FBut unions said the proposed bill was  
OL,19,F"undemocratic, unworkable, and almost  
OL,20,Fcertainly illegal".                    
